# --- Hyperledger Fabric Binaries and Config ---
**/bin/
**/config/
**/builders/

# --- Generated Runtime Artifacts ---
# These are environment-specific and should never be committed
**/channel-artifacts/
**/system-genesis-block/*.block
**/*.block
**/*.json
**/*.pb
**/*.tx
**/log.txt
**/*.log
**/*.tar.gz
**/*.gz

# Keep system genesis directory structure for channel bootstrap
!**/system-genesis-block/.gitkeep

# --- Cryptographic Materials (Security Sensitive) ---
# Never commit private keys, MSP certs, or TLS artifacts
**/organizations/peerOrganizations/
**/organizations/ordererOrganizations/

# Handle Fabric CA generated data carefully
**/organizations/fabric-ca/*/msp/
**/organizations/fabric-ca/*/tls-cert.pem
**/organizations/fabric-ca/*/ca-cert.pem
**/organizations/fabric-ca/*/Issuer*
**/organizations/fabric-ca/*/*.db
**/organizations/fabric-ca/*/tls/

# Exception: keep CA configuration templates and scripts
!**/organizations/fabric-ca/registerEnroll.sh
!**/organizations/fabric-ca/ordererOrg/fabric-ca-server-config.yaml
!**/organizations/fabric-ca/manufacturer/fabric-ca-server-config.yaml
!**/organizations/fabric-ca/showroom/fabric-ca-server-config.yaml
!**/addCustomer/fabric-ca/customer/fabric-ca-server-config.yaml

# Never commit private key material (fail-safe)
**/keystore/*
**/*_sk

# --- Service-Specific Data ---

# Hyperledger Explorer
**/explorer/.env
**/explorer/.env.*
!**/explorer/.env.example
**/explorer/wallet/
**/explorer/data/

# Monitoring (Prometheus/Grafana)
**/prometheus-grafana/grafana_db/*.db
**/prometheus-grafana/prometheus/data/

# --- Standard Development Artifacts ---
node_modules/
**/vendor/
.idea/
.vscode/
.DS_Store
*.swp
*.bak